### Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/users/1

###

### Get another user
GET http://localhost:3000/users/42

###

### Create new user
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com"
}

